snippet.title: Rhodri Giggs Show #14 | Messi Wins Balon D'or | But Should he have won? | Rangick confirmed & more
snippet.description:
Welcome to our brand new Live and Exclusive series ' Rhodri Giggs on Football'.  Where the boys tackle the biggest and most interesting stories in football each week.

A.C.E Podcast Nation presents Rhodri Giggs on Football

This week A.C.E Podcast Nation Host & Founder Si (@ACEcast_Nation) and Ex Salford City winger Rhodri Giggs discuss the biggest stories of the week from the beautiful game as the season is in full flow the lads break it all down and you can have your say in real time as we are Live every Friday 7pm (UK) 2pm(EST) on three platforms.

This week Si and Rhodri will be talking the ups and downs for of the beautiful game, Messi Wins Balon D'or, but Should he have won?, Rangick confirmed and the Latest news from the football world and a whole lot more including tackling the questions from the live chat.

Rhodri Giggs on Football is exclusively Live every Friday 7.30pm on A.C.E Podcast Nation (@ACEPodcastNationOfficial)
